Uses of Package
aom.scripting.datatypes

Packages that use aom.scripting.datatypes
Package Description
aom.scripting.anim
This package contains a list of possible Logics that can be used in animation scripts.
aom.scripting.datatypes
This package contains primitive type definitions used in XS that are not native to java.
aom.scripting.ui
This package contains classes describing the basic structure of UI files.
aom.scripting.ui.config
This package contains configuration flags and related functions.
aom.scripting.ui.console
This package contains classes with constants and functions that can be executed in UI scripts, in Hotkeys and in the Console.
aom.scripting.xs.ai
This package contains classes with constants and functions that can be executed in AI scripts.
aom.scripting.xs.kb
This package contains classes with constants and functions that can be executed in AI, TR and VC scripts.
aom.scripting.xs.rm
This package contains classes with constants and functions that can be executed in RM scripts.
aom.scripting.xs.tr
This package contains classes with constants and functions that can be executed in TR and VC scripts.
aom.scripting.xs.tr.addons
This package contains classes with constants and functions that are part of trigger extension frameworks.
aom.scripting.xs.xs
This package contains classes with constants and functions that can be executed in AI, TR and VC scripts.
